---
title: Veggie Ragu Pasta Bake with Peppers and Mushrooms
description: You won’t miss the meat in our veggie ragu pasta bake. Made with a rich, tomatoey sauce, red lentils and stringy, melted mozzarella, this is every pasta lover’s dream!
